&lt;h2&gt;Use Anaconda&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anaconda allows to have multiple python versions. This is much easier than using &lt;em&gt;virtualenv&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_ed8a94a63c0e4fafabf38d9f6c9eebf0-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;conda env list &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# lists all envs&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_ed8a94a63c0e4fafabf38d9f6c9eebf0-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;conda env create py3.5 pip setuptools &lt;span class="nv"&gt;python&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="m"&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;.5 &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# create a python env&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_ed8a94a63c0e4fafabf38d9f6c9eebf0-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;conda activate py3.5 &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# activate the latter&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_ed8a94a63c0e4fafabf38d9f6c9eebf0-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;conda deactivate &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# deactivate it&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_ed8a94a63c0e4fafabf38d9f6c9eebf0-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;conda env remove -n py3.5 &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# remove it completely&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="section" id="use-pip-together-with-anaconda"&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Use pip together with anaconda&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The package will be installed within the environement. pip has a much broader
list of packages than the anaconda channel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="code bash"&gt;&lt;a name="rest_code_34e17b7b53384fe5974b61e8c23bfa9a-1"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install &amp;lt;my-package&amp;gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# install a package&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_34e17b7b53384fe5974b61e8c23bfa9a-2"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install
&lt;a name="rest_code_34e17b7b53384fe5974b61e8c23bfa9a-3"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install --index-url https://pypi.org/simple/ &amp;lt;my-package&amp;gt; &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# specify the repository&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_34e17b7b53384fe5974b61e8c23bfa9a-4"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip install . &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# a local package&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;a name="rest_code_34e17b7b53384fe5974b61e8c23bfa9a-5"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;pip remove &amp;lt;my-package&amp;gt;  &lt;span class="c1"&gt;# remove it&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><guid>https://parisni.github.io/weblog/posts/a-decent-python-configuration/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 11 Nov 2018 10:43:34 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>